					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Celius wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">How do you tell the ROM to use the CHR bit for PRG bankswitching?</div>
<br />
<br />You make the PRG ROM 512KB long. Seriously, this is how most (if not all) emulators support the NES-SUROM board when presented as iNES mapper 1.</div>

					
